          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "When it comes to cars engineered to last, few companies have been as consistent as Mercedes-Benz. Back in the 1970s its advertising slogan was ‘Engineered like no ",
